Package edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.universe.common Description

Implementations of SymbolicUniverses. Most of the services are already provided by edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.preuniverse.IF, and edu.udel.cis.vsl.sarl.reason.IF, so there is only a little bit more here to bring the pieces together.
